reviews.review_text:
Good Stuff! While probably not the best performance of the year, this is an excellent show.
Great versions of Workingman's material as well as a fantastic Cosmic Charlie and one of my favourite versions of Mason's among other highlights.

Zachariah I agree with other reviewer, this may not be their best of '70 but it was easily their best of the year up to that point, only 3 days in  ;)  Small cuts, beautiful Wolf, but overall solid quality. Made my grey day here a bit brighter. Rosy red & electric blue 4****

Thank you Archive & Green Mountain Bros

P.S. at the begining of Mason's they talk about a movie they wrote the song for. The title was Zachariah.
